## Oracle Cloud VPS Optimization Script

This software is designed to optimize Oracle Cloud VPS servers for better performance,
security, and resource management.

### Features Included:
- Memory optimization with ZRAM compression
- Storage optimization with I/O scheduler tuning
- Network optimization with BBR congestion control
- Security hardening with firewall and fail2ban
- System cleanup and maintenance tasks
- Performance benchmarking and monitoring

### Supported Systems:
- Debian 9+
- Ubuntu 16.04+
- RHEL/CentOS 7+
- Oracle Linux 7+

For more information, please visit:
https://github.com/youming-ai/oracle-cloud-setup
